{"tid":2530911,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"王浩信又扮盲！　殺入電影界做男主角為影帝舖路？","createTime":"2021-05-14T20:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-14T21:20:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e97dc5477d3df6b159805ac1af7d1c47f0ce0575","tid":2530911,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T20:06:53.000Z","msg":"5月13日電影《見怪》亮相愛奇藝世界大會年度新片發布現場，概念海報首度發布，金像獎金牌製作班底，朱嘉懿監製，孔令政執導，王浩信和陳啓泰領銜主演，馬志威友情演出。宣傳口號是驚悚巨獸，突襲荒島，「切勿睜開雙眼」！<br />\n<br />\n王浩信在社交平台指：「今次對我來講真係盲出個新高度，演出時失去九成九嘅視覺，非常高興和大家合作，雖然每天泥濘，但每日收工都好滿足！非常期待製成品！」王浩信在兩輯《踩過界》飾演「盲俠」大獲好評，今次跳入電影界依然要扮「盲」，唔知會唔會再有突破呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210514/469952544408342528126587.jpeg/dD4-p6RAvcfRYeYCZ-F8iAfsC-Fm3-XhNwvMsjcLzLI?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210514%2F469952544408342528126587.jpeg%2FdD4-p6RAvcfRYeYCZ-F8iAfsC-Fm3-XhNwvMsjcLzLI%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=56e44ae6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"660f9d9f2f6b229448929375b5791551c2ff3107","tid":2530911,"uid":190789,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T20:10:01.000Z","msg":"Yoyo咁正都偷食 真人盲撚咗好耐"},{"pid":"337e7962f956804124629ce411de638d6be9befe","tid":2530911,"uid":60145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"660f9d9f2f6b229448929375b5791551c2ff3107","tid":2530911,"uid":190789,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T20:10:01.000Z","msg":"Yoyo咁正都偷食 真人盲撚咗好耐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T20:37:02.000Z","msg":"偷食都算<br />\n仲要偷食條女仲衰過自己老婆先係問題"},{"pid":"bb8235411dbaa1632a12f68e32aa7b190d433a66","tid":2530911,"uid":96704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"660f9d9f2f6b229448929375b5791551c2ff3107","tid":2530911,"uid":190789,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T20:10:01.000Z","msg":"Yoyo咁正都偷食 真人盲撚咗好耐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T21:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\